{"type":"message","id":"a14cea22","parentId":"95208905","timestamp":"2026-03-19T05:32:01.010Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The context usage is at 65%, which exceeds the 60% threshold. According to the skill, I should trigger a seamless session switch. Let me check the current session status to understand what's happening, and then proceed with the switch.\n\nActually, I need to understand - this is an automatic context manager. The script has detected 65% usage, which exceeds the 60% threshold. According to the skill:\n- 60% threshold triggers automatic session switch\n- Should save memory and create new session\n\nLet me check the session status and see what's the current state, then determine if I need to trigger a switch.","thinkingSignature":"14026bb962989492d92b7e968938dc26845df6cbddf2d5e4573bafc5bb512a40"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_qm1q5zsv4t0f_1","name":"session_status","arguments":{}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":3055,"output":143,"cacheRead":37002,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":40200,"cost":{"input":0.0009165,"output":0.0001716,"cacheRead":0.00111006,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0021981600000000002}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773898316128}}
