{"type":"message","id":"f631268c","parentId":"a053ea45","timestamp":"2026-03-19T05:32:22.242Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_uax3wqu9uuiu_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# MEMORY.md — Long-Term Memory\r\n\r\n## About Sir\r\n- **Name:** Sir\r\n- **What to call them:** Sir\r\n- **Timezone:** Asia/Shanghai (GMT+8)\r\n- **Preferences:** 专业、高效、略带英式管家的优雅\r\n\r\n## Active Projects\r\n- OpenClaw 配置和技能安装\r\n- 系统备份和恢复流程\r\n\r\n## Decisions & Lessons\r\n- 使用 ClawHub 管理技能\r\n- 定期备份 workspace 到 D 盘\r\n- 配置 Self-Improving 和 Proactivity 提升执行质量\r\n\r\n## Preferences\r\n- **Communication style:** 简洁、专业、不过于正式\r\n- **Tools:** ClawHub、Tavily Search、Multi-Search-Engine\r\n- **Workflows:** 先审查再安装技能，定期备份\r\n\r\n## Installed Skills\r\n- skill-finder-cn\r\n- openclaw-tavily-search (已配置 API)\r\n- multi-search-engine\r\n- office-automation-test\r\n- cron-mastery\r\n- news-summary\r\n- free-ride\r\n- browser-automation\r\n- desktop-control-win\r\n- self-improving (已配置)\r\n- proactivity (已配置)\r\n- skill-vetter\r\n- memory-setup\r\n\r\n## System Info\r\n- **OS:** Windows 10/11\r\n- **Shell:** PowerShell\r\n- **Python:** 3.11.9\r\n- **OpenClaw Version:** 2026.3.13\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773898342241}}
